            %span 3分
            ですぐに出品
            .toppage__main__introduction__reasons__reason__text-coment スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
        .toppage__main__introduction__reasons__reason
          .toppage__main__introduction__reasons__reason-image
            .toppage__main__introduction__reasons__reason-image__number 2
            = image_tag "simple.jpg", size: "295x295"
          .toppage__main__introduction__reasons__reason__text
            %span シンプル
