            = image_tag "app-store.svg", size: "180x54"
          .toppage__main__middle-image__content__install__google-play
            = image_tag "google-play.svg", size: "180x54"
    .toppage__main__middle-content
      .toppage__main__middle-content__title FURIMAの特徴
      .toppage__main__middle-content__features
        .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature
          .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature__image
            = image_tag "easy.png", size: "244x333"
          .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature__text 簡単に売り買いできる
          .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature__detail スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
        .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature
          .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature__image
            = image_tag "speed.png", size: "244x333"
          .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature__text 売上金は即日振込みに対応
          .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature__detail 午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!
        .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature
          .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature__image
            = image_tag "pay.png", size: "244x333"
          .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature__text 様々な支払いに対応
          .toppage__main__middle-content__features__feature__detail お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。
